text: Þis wæs gedon ymbeVIIIInigon hund wintra &LXVIIII& on nigoþan geare þe Oswold bisceop to folgoðe feng.
Sancta Maria & sanctus Michahel cum sancto Petro & eallum Godes halgum gemiltsie þis healdendum.
Gif hwa butan gewyrhtum hit abrecan wylle hæbbe him wið God gemære buton he ær to dædbote gecyrre.
Þis syndon þa landgemæru twegra hida æt Stoce.
Ærest on æscwellan, of æscwellan west on þa halas þanon on dynninces grafes wyrttruman<../images/tbar.gif>swa on swepelan stream.
Of swepelan streame west be wudu riman on readan wege.
Suðweardan of readan wege west eft in æsc wellan.
